(162, 10,N'A wonderful journey with beautiful scenery, creatures, and concepts. This is truly a marvelous experience. However, as a game, it has many downsides, especially with frustrating controls and gameplay where a single mistake can cost you a lot of time. Although some of the puzzles you have to solve to defeat the colossi were pretty fun.',N'2024-12-12'),
