(167, 4,N'Tbh i found this game to be long and tedious. The story was forgettable and i thought the gameplay was okay but not really the best, just found it pretty boring half of the time. In all honesty, I dont understand why they would even make this game (1 point cause of how cool some of the character designs were)',N'2025-05-02'),
(167, 3,N'The closest a Warriors game gets to being interesting but unfortunately this still suffers from the same fate other Warriors games do, the gameplay gets too repetitive and is NOT interesting enough to not get stale by the end of the game. Still, merging the Persona skill system with this style was pretty well done, so it gets points there and the story is... alright, its about what youd expect for a spinoff title, certainly not as good as mainline Persona stories but okay for what it is, the new characters are quite nice, especially Zenkichi. Basically, its okay but only just okay. Soundtrack is hard, naturally, Last Surprise -Strikers- is even better than base Last Surprise.',N'2025-05-25'),
