(320, 1,N'coming back to this game over a year later to play the dlc was a whole new experience. gone was the player who once knew how to play this game, who had spent hours painstakingly devising the most efficient system of farming every resource. gone was the player who carefully memorised her process of elimination method to discover all the new recipes. gone was the player who knew where literally anything was.',N'2024-04-03'),
