(328, 3,N'I cant shake the feeling that I am thoroughly bored playing Hades. Ive picked up Hades three times over the last few years, and three times Ive found myself putting down the controller after a handful of hours, especially after reaching the third stage, and I couldnt figure out why it wasnt working for me. After giving it a few good goes, Ive finally managed to pin down what it is that just doesnt click for me about Hades.',N'2025-11-06'),
