(370, 3,N'the most engaging puzzles/riddles ive ever seen in a game. solutions are very clever but not unfair. exploring the planets and their ruins and stumbling on all kinds of crazy shit is a great time, and unraveling the mystery one step at a time so you can piece together the bigger picture is incredibly satisfying. the environment design is also amazing and the concepts in the later portions of the game are so cool and interesting, cant elaborate because of spoilers. the dlc is just okay though ngl, exploring the setting was cool but it felt like a lot of running around doing busy work for very little reward',N'2024-12-28'),
