(526, 4,N'Yeah this game is great, it improves on the original in almost every conceivable way. The writing is better, the gameplay has more QOL features and is faster and smoother, the world is more interesting to explore, theres a better overarching story thats surprisingly emotional by the end amongst other things.',N'2024-02-04'),
