(534, 6,N'(Played before 2023)\n                     \n                     This is probably the best non-combat horror game Ive played, but I really hate non-combat horror games because it takes away a lot of choices you can make which makes it scarier. To me, it isnt that scary gameplay-wise when my only option is to run down a hallway and hide in a locker or a bed. The asylum is a cliche but fun setting, but Im not that impressed with the game like a lot of other peple are. I think it just came out at a good time where most of thse type of games (and still now) were cheap, lazy works or were created by one single person.',N'2025-08-06'),
