(607, 5,N'I dont think this game is nearly as bad as everyone tries to make it out to be, it tries to follow in the footsteps of the original DS NSMB except with a gimmick of just shoving coins literally everywhere, which yeah is kinda a bland/lame gimmick but really I felt like when actually playing the coins were only as prevalent as something like rings in sonic, which is to say they are everywhere but not absurdly so. The thing about the NSMB games is that they arent bad they are just painfully generic, so its good at the very least to see nintendo TRY to do something different with the formula, even if it was something as shallow as making the game full of coins.',N'2024-03-14'),
