(693, 9,N'if something like mario land 1 or 64DS is the shrek the third of the mario franchise, origami king is the shark tale. it is utterly and completely baffling in how poorly some things were handled, an awful game with awful executions for what would otherwise be okay ideas. but I just can\t keep myself away from it because it\s badness is so fascinating and the good bits are genuinely really good',N'2025-10-31'),
